divs: Sighting Detailsleft my neighbors house - walking home - saw plane in sky - caught sight of something out of left eye - saw the largest v shaped thing ever- some forward lights lit, some not (huge) cannot say what it was, but would bet it was not terrestial, if that means not of this earth love to watch the skies, always thought we were alone. not too sure now. tried to get my husband to see craft, he was in shower - by time i got back to neighbor, it was gone.
Summary: saw a large v shaped object in the sky that flew over head
